comments: Williamson (NOP) maintains a legal guarding position on Fox (SAC) during his spin move at the start of the drive.
Holmes (SAC) makes contact with Ingram's (NOP) body during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Hernangomez (NOP) enters the lane prior to the release of the free throw.
Holmes (SAC) establishes himself in a screening position in Ingram's (NOP) path and absorbs the contact.
During the rebound, Hernangomez (NOP) briefly grasps and immediately releases Holmes' (SAC) jersey without affecting his FOM.
Hield (SAC) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Ball (NOP).
Holmes (SAC) blocks the shot attempt by Ball (NOP), which has a chance to score, after it makes contact with the backboard.
Ball (NOP) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Fox (SAC).
Hernangomez (NOP) is in the lane for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.

Hernangomez (NOP) reaches for the loose ball and returns to the ground as incidental contact occurs with Hield (SAC).  Hield loses his balance on his own and not as a result of contact with Hernangomez.
Ball (NOP) is retreating with an already extended arm that he places on Fox's (SAC) body without delivering contact during his driving shot attempt.
Fox (SAC) legally contests Ingram's (NOP) jump shot attempt.
Hart (NOP) commits a take foul on Haliburton (SAC).
During the inbound, Williamson (NOP) and Holmes (SAC) engage and disengage and the contact is marginal.
Ball (NOP) reaches across Hield's (SAC) body and makes contact to his shoulder prior to the ball.
Ingram (NOP) maintains a legal guarding position on Barnes (SAC) as he avoids the trap and brings the ball up the court.
Bledsoe (NOP) commits a take foul on Hield (SAC).
Fox (SAC) legally contests Bledsoe's (NOP) jump shot attempt.
